      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a deep way to look at it. I definitely want to be respectful. But if I'm looking at the actual clothes and the visual stuff for the mood board, what are the specific visual \"staples\" or vibes that define that look? Like, what are the key elements that communicate that \"urban\" identity visually?",
